This project is a clean-room MVP inspired by the architecture and vocabulary of
Autogenesis ("a self-evolution protocol and runtime for LLM-based agent
systems"):

    Autogenesis — https://github.com/DVampire/Autogenesis  (MIT License)

GNSIS reimplements a small, stable subset of those ideas — the RSPL (versioned
resources) and SEPL (the self-evolution loop) concepts and the tool-calling
agent — from scratch. No Autogenesis source code is vendored here.
